<br>
Secondarily, it is almost impossible to go get more mobs for your swarm kite AND continue the process of swarming. Your pet will be too far away (stationary) while you go off for respawn. So instead of halting the process 9, 10, or even an innumerable number of times, it's best to halt the process only once (when you have no mobs left ion your kite), get the entire respawn, and begin again.<br>
<br>
Your last point about him not being in the zone is unsupported by the evidence from either side. Had that been the case -t-that he left the zone - the mobs in his kite would have wandered back and killed the group on the way. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=largthemiserable>Largthemiserable</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>l33t board camper</span><br>  Posts: 307<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/5/03 6:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1599.topic&index=79>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Wow, homo bards really do hold onto bad arguments long after they lose the battle.  You see, maybe on your server bards are allowed to be dipshits and that sets the standard for you, but in this case, you have a person, not on your server, who is being judged on what is known as the &quot;common sense scale&quot;.  No fucking excuses for not being able to type or stay in one area.  If you're not there, not in the area of the camp, shit's up, and not responding to any form of camp checking, you're not fucking camping the spawn.  Period.  If it's different on your server, your server has set some gay fucking standards.  Here, if you're a dipshit, trainer, jackass, retard, or just a faggot bard that can't control, in some sense, the area in which they need to circle jerk with their pull, they get no mercy here. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=reallylongtypist>ReallyLongTypist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/5/03 8:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10